These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Job: entrepreneur, analyst, project-manager, lawyer
1. Job:lawyer is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Job:analyst##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Job:project-manager is on the left or right of Job:lawyer##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Job        | entrepreneur | analyst   | lawyer | project-manager    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Flower: balloon-flower, aconite, daffodil, sunflower
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:daffodil##1
3. Flower:daffodil is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:balloon-flower == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Flower:aconite is on the right of Flower:daffodil##1
6. Flower:balloon-flower == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Flower   | sunflower    | balloon-flower | daffodil | aconite    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Flower: aconite, azalea, begonia, balloon-flower
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Flower:begonia is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Flower:azalea##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Flower:azalea is on the right of Flower:begonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower | begonia | azalea    | aconite      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

