2. Pet:mouse == Music-Genre:punk##1
3. Pet:goat is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:jazz is in an odd position##4
6. Pet:frog is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Pet   | frog | fish | goat | mouse |

